::KitKat::

She suddenly rememberd the clone.  She ordered the clone to go her 
quarters and go into rest position and wait for her there.  She 
didn't want the others to see the clone and shoot it up. Not before 
she had a chance to use it.

The clone walked down the hallways and went into KitKat's quarters.  
The clone was rather large and it was a bit of a tight fit, but he 
made it inside and waited.
